{"id": 2088, "genre": 1000, "title": "你对现如今的公益慈善活动都有什么不满意？", "description": "但很多情况下，更好的方式难以推进，这些问题又一次次出现。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 5889, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171226112746inq82B1rEcIVlY6F.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-26T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3478, "title": "你对现如今的公益慈善活动都有什么不满意？", "content": "现如今各种和公益有关的活动，可能会出现哪些问题？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 256538, "content": "鼓动大家买滞销农产品，实际可能是电商营销", "image": "img/option/option/20171226142533P9DX0fJdZYWg1vxL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 256540, "content": "重病募捐，即便有所谓平台审核也难判断需求迫切性", "image": "img/option/option/20171226142852A6kNgo3qfOEnHx24.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 256541, "content": "寻找走失儿童老人，大部分时候人们转发完就不管了", "image": "img/option/option/20171226143312btNw9kUP0OTduVgn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 256544, "content": "为贫困儿童募集衣服文具，没截止时间和数量，最后供过于求", "image": "img/option/option/20171226144655hjr3ftVxScdK1q08.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 256546, "content": "在社交网络传播自己能提供的帮助，目标受众看不到", "image": "img/option/option/201712261450035mqXGBOcxsoPzJvT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 256549, "content": "宣扬公益旅行，实际上把支教/支援贫困区当体验生活", "image": "img/option/option/20171226145452CDL0B1pFxXd4UfR5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 256550, "content": "花式宣传、设计活动，但关注点偏离需要帮助的人", "image": "img/option/option/20171226145514ag64wE7f3jCAWShr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 256552, "content": "提供帮助之后用途明细不透明，不明确告知如何跟进", "image": "img/option/option/20171226145919qtTyuCRK2flPO8nz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}